articles.title: Dare County reports first bird flu case in backyard flock of chickens - WRAL News
articles.description: A backyard flock of chickens in Dare County has tested positive for bird flu, prompting the euthanasia of the birds to prevent further spread.
articles.content:
A Dare County resident had
to sacrifice their backyard chickens after the birds tested positive for the
bird flu.
